S.FORM: Jovenel Moïse I 1968 a miheca saka 6 folad saka 26 a romi'ad masofoc ci Jovenel Moïse, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Haiti anini i ci Jovenel Moïse, patirengan a romi'ad i 2017 a miheca saka 2 folad saka 7 a romi'ad.
